        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Workforce Investment Act of 1998/s:136/ss:b/p:2/sp:A/cl:i/scl:III">subclause (III)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking <quote>and</quote>;</text>
      </paragraph>
